OL,6,FBristol Royal Infirmary (BRI) has
OL,7,Fstood down its 'critical incident' as
OL,8,Fpower is restored to Bristol city
OL,9,Fcentre hospitals.
OL,11,FPeople were asked not to attend the
OL,12,Fhospital yesterday after University
OL,13,FHospitals Bristol and Weston NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust said "a power outage"
OL,15,Fis affecting its hospitals in Bristol
OL,16,Fcity centre.
