OL,6,FThe Trust runs multiple sites in the
OL,7,Fcentre of the city including the BRI,
OL,8,FBristol Royal Hospital for Children,
OL,9,FSt Michael's Hospital and Bristol Eye
OL,10,FHospital.
OL,12,FIn a statement, interim chief medical
OL,13,Fofficer at UHBW Dr Rebecca Maxwell
OL,14,Fsaid: "We have declared a critical
OL,15,Fincident due to a power outage. We aim
OL,16,Fto have this fully resolved as soon as
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,19,F"I would like to share with the public
OL,20,Fthat every single patient, visitor and
OL,21,Fcolleagues are safe.
