OL,6,F"Our adult emergency department is
OL,7,Fcurrently closed to patients but the
OL,8,Fchildren's emergency department is
OL,9,Fopen.
OL,11,F"We ask the public not to attend our
OL,12,FBristol city centre hospitals until
OL,13,Fthe incident is resolved and use
OL,14,Falternative services in the area.
OL,16,F"We have an emergency power back-up
OL,17,Fgenerator that is supplying a lot of
OL,18,Fpower to the hospital and we're
OL,19,Fbringing more generators in to support
OL,20,Fthat.
