OL,6,F"One or two areas in the hospital do
OL,7,Fnot have lights at the moment and one
OL,8,Fof those is part of the adult
OL,9,Femergency department which is closed
OL,10,Fto new patients."
OL,12,FAt 9:18pm Dr Rebecca Maxwell said:
OL,13,F"Our adult Emergency Department is now
OL,14,Fopen to urgent walk-in patients. Our
OL,15,FChildren's Emergency Department
OL,16,Fremains open to both ambulances and
OL,17,Fwalk-in patients.
