OL,6,F"If you have a life threatening
OL,7,Femergency please dial 999, for any
OL,8,Fother urgent medical advice please use
OL,9,F.
OL,11,F"Some of our sites continue to be
OL,12,Fimpacted by the power outage and we
OL,13,Fare working to resolve the situation
OL,14,Fas quickly as possible. Thank you for
OL,15,Fyour patience."
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the police said the
OL,18,Fincident is believed to be caused by
OL,19,Fan electrical fault.
