OL,6,FAt 10:15am on Saturday 4 May, Dr
OL,7,FRebecca Maxwell, Interim Chief Medical
OL,8,FOfficer at UHBW said: "Power has now
OL,9,Fbeen fully restored to all of our
OL,10,Fhospitals, and we remain in internal
OL,11,Fcritical incident as we carefully
OL,12,Freset and restore our services.
OL,14,F"Our adult Emergency Department is now
OL,15,Fopen to both ambulances and urgent
OL,16,Fwalk-in patients. Our Children's
OL,17,FEmergency Department continues to be
OL,18,Fopen to both ambulances and walk-in
OL,19,Fpatients.
