OL,6,F"Patients with appointments should
OL,7,Fattend as planned unless we have
OL,8,Fcontacted them directly, and we
OL,9,Fwelcome visitors back to our hospitals.
OL,11,F"The safety of our patients and
OL,12,Fcolleagues has been maintained
OL,13,Fthroughout thanks to the amazing
OL,14,Fefforts of our staff, emergency
OL,15,Fservices and healthcare partners."
