OL,6,FAn update on Saturday 4 May at 2:30pm
OL,7,Ffrom Dr Rebecca Maxwell, Interim Chief
OL,8,FMedical Officer at UHBW said: "Thanks
OL,9,Fto the amazing efforts of our
OL,10,Fcolleagues, we have made good progress
OL,11,Fin restoring our services and have now
OL,12,Fstood down our Internal Critical
OL,13,FIncident.
OL,15,F"Our Emergency Departments are open
OL,16,Ffor urgent and emergency patients.
OL,17,FPatients with appointments should
OL,18,Fattend as planned unless we have
OL,19,Fcontacted them directly, and we
OL,20,Fwelcome visitors back to our
OL,21,Fhospitals."
